Miscellany
----------
	This program is written by a Siebel developer and may have tens 
	of improvisations that everyone else in the world considers 
	'must-have'. 
	>> It is created using the excellent Microsoft (c) Visual Basic .NET
	platform. 
	>> It uses the light-weight editor 'metapad' (details below) to
	display the file content.


